inspiration: art should comfort the disturbed and disturb the comfortable by caesar cruz, but heard from nightmoire

last night she thought she might take the day off but now.. as she sits on the side of the bed looking at the table, she thinks it's prolly better to not be alone w her thoughts today, not that she thought she'd be alone today. 
"That's what I get for taking things for granted.. I guess.."
she looks at her rings on the night stand... those rings that were her mask since she was little and she thinks that today, they might break her fingers if she puts them on, she thinks that maybe, this time.. they won't work. but she takes a deep breath, says his name in her mind and then out loud, 
"Leo, I'll stretch myself to hold both you and this ache I only have myself to blame."
she takes the rings and puts them on, washes her armpits in the bathroom sink, and looks at the bidet.. maybe she could just keep him on her... just a bit longer. but then she feels the ring on her index finger, empties her mind, sits on the bidet and washes him off, brushes her teeth and puts her hair in a bun, pulls up her panties, throws the stockings in the bin, looks at her legs and thinks.. maybe I should give them a shave.. in the right light.. it's noticeable, but there's no time, she pulls her skirt up and shoves her feet in her heels, puts her blouse on and the jacket and takes one more look at the room. 
"you should take a picture, it lasts longer" she remembers telling leo that time she caught him looking at her. 
she picks up her purse and closes the door behind her. when she gets at her car she goes in, but her legs are trembling. she can't leave the car at the hotel tho. "get a fucking grip Bea" and as she says this she sees the skin of his neck, every pore, every hair, his smell, and she blushes. she wants to run. she wants to run to the moon and back. her legs stop shaking, she turns on the radio and the car and goes to work
"I can be frail later"

before she gets out of the car she checks to see if she smells of sweat. "I should be ok w the jacket.. plus I think I have another jacket in the office..."
she takes the elevator and passes the coffee machine and she stops for a coffee
"yeah she's definitely writing something on company time, and right under her bosses nose. clearly bea is clueless or she would fire her if she knew." 

